function getQueryString(name) {
	var reg = new RegExp("(^|&)" + name + "=([^&]*)(&|$)", "i");
	var r = window.location.search.substr(1).match(reg);
	if (r != null) {
 return unescape(r[2]);
	}
	return null;
}
var src = getQueryString("source");
var sp = document.getElementById("sp_err");

	sp.innerHTML = "\u7528\u6237\u5bc6\u7801\u9519\u8bef";
	sp.style.display = "";
} else {
	if (getQueryString("error") == "idnull") {
 sp.innerHTML = "\u8be5\u5e10\u6237\u4e0d\u5b58\u5728";
 sp.style.display = "";
	} else {
 if (getQueryString("error") == "msg") {
	sp.innerHTML = "\u767b\u5f55\u540e\u7ee7\u7eed\u64cd\u4f5c";
	sp.style.display = "";
 } else {
	if (getQueryString("error") == "iddel") {
 sp.innerHTML = "\u8fdd\u89c4\u7528\u6237\uff0c\u5df2\u88ab\u6ce8\u9500";
 sp.style.display = "";
	} else {
 sp.style.display = "none";

	}
 }
	}
}

	var key3 = "pfir";

	document.getElementById("j_passdec").value = enResult;
	return true;

o=0,l=0,h=0,f=0,e=0;for(h=0;h<32;h++){c[h]=p[h];s[h]=p[32+h]}for(o=15;o>=0;o--){for(l=0;l<32;l++){g[l]=c[l];c[l]=s[l]}var r=new Array(48);for(f=0;f<48;f++){r[f]=t[o][f]}var a=xor(pPermute(sBoxPermute(xor(expandPermute(s),r))),g);for(e=0;e<32;e++){s[e]=a[e]}}var d=new Array(64);for(o=0;o<32;o++){d[o]=s[o];d[32+o]=c[o]}return finallyPermute(d)}function initPermute(b){var a=new Array(64);for(i=0,m=1,n=0;i<4;i++,m+=2,n+=2){for(j=7,k=0;j>=0;j--,k++){a[i*8+k]=b[j*8+m];a[i*8+k+32]=b[j*8+n]}}return a}function expandPermute(a){var b=new Array(48);for(i=0;i<8;i++){if(i==0){b[i*6+0]=a[31]}else{b[i*6+0]=a[i*4-1]}b[i*6+1]=a[i*4+0];b[i*6+2]=a[i*4+1];b[i*6+3]=a[i*4+2];b[i*6+4]=a[i*4+3];if(i==7){b[i*6+5]=a[0]}else{b[i*6+5]=a[i*4+4]}}return b}function xor(c,b){var a=new Array(c.length);for(i=0;i<c.length;i++){a[i]=c[i]^b[i]}return a}function sBoxPermute(c){var a=new Array(32);var e="";var r=[[14,4,13,1,2,15,11,8,3,10,6,12,5,9,0,7],[0,15,7,4,14,2,13,1,10,6,12,11,9,5,3,8],[4,1,14,8,13,6,2,11,15,12,9,7,3,10,5,0],[15,12,8,2,4,9,1,7,5,11,3,14,10,0,6,13]];var q=[[15,1,8,14,6,11,3,4,9,7,2,13,12,0,5,10],[3,13,4,7,15,2,8,14,12,0,1,10,6,9,11,5],[0,14,7,11,10,4,13,1,5,8,12,6,9,3,2,15],[13,8,10,1,3,15,4,2,11,6,7,12,0,5,14,9]];var p=[[10,0,9,14,6,3,15,5,1,13,12,7,11,4,2,8],[13,7,0,9,3,4,6,10,2,8,5,14,12,11,15,1],[13,6,4,9,8,15,3,0,11,1,2,12,5,10,14,7],[1,10,13,0,6,9,8,7,4,15,14,3,11,5,2,12]];var o=[[7,13,14,3,0,6,9,10,1,2,8,5,11,12,4,15],[13,8,11,5,6,15,0,3,4,7,2,12,1,10,14,9],[10,6,9,0,12,11,7,13,15,1,3,14,5,2,8,4],[3,15,0,6,10,1,13,8,9,4,5,11,12,7,2,14]];var l=[[2,12,4,1,7,10,11,6,8,5,3,15,13,0,14,9],[14,11,2,12,4,7,13,1,5,0,15,10,3,9,8,6],[4,2,1,11,10,13,7,8,15,9,12,5,6,3,0,14],[11,8,12,7,1,14,2,13,6,15,0,9,10,4,5,3]];var h=[[12,1,10,15,9,2,6,8,0,13,3,4,14,7,5,11],[10,15,4,2,7,12,9,5,6,1,13,14,0,11,3,8],[9,14,15,5,2,8,12,3,7,0,4,10,1,13,11,6],[4,3,2,12,9,5,15,10,11,14,1,7,6,0,8,13]];var g=[[4,11,2,14,15,0,8,13,3,12,9,7,5,10,6,1],[13,0,11,7,4,9,1,10,14,3,5,12,2,15,8,6],[1,4,11,13,12,3,7,14,10,15,6,8,0,5,9,2],[6,11,13,8,1,4,10,7,9,5,0,15,14,2,3,12]];var f=[[13,2,8,4,6,15,11,1,10,9,3,14,5,0,12,7],[1,15,13,8,10,3,7,4,12,5,6,11,0,14,9,2],[7,11,4,1,9,12,14,2,0,6,10,13,15,3,5,8],[2,1,14,7,4,10,8,13,15,12,9,0,3,5,6,11]];for(m=0;m<8;m++){var 7:e=getBoxBinary(f[d][b]);break}a[m*4+0]=parseInt(e.substring(0,1));a[m*4+1]=parseInt(e.substring(1,2));a[m*4+2]=parseInt(e.substring(2,3));a[m*4+3]=parseInt(e.substring(3,4))}return a}function pPermute(b){var a=new 14:b="1110";break;case 15:b="1111";break}return b}function generateKeys(c){var e=new Array(56);var f=new Array();f[0]=new Array();f[1]=new Array();f[2]=new Array();f[3]=new Array();f[4]=new b=0;for(j=0;j<a[d];j++){h=e[0];b=e[28];for(k=0;k<27;k++){e[k]=e[k+1];e[28+k]=e[29+k]}e[27]=h;e[55]=b}var g=new     for(var i=1; i<=n;i++){
   $("#"+tabname+i).attr("class","");

	<script>
 var account = "lqlz";
 
 if (account == null || account == "") {

	var logincookie = CookieUtil.get("STOKEN");

	if (logincookie != null && logincookie != "") {

  if (checkdate(logincookie.split("/")[1])) {

	          var currentUrl = window.location.href;

	          CookieUtil.set("H_U", currentUrl, "/", "/", null, true);

	          window.location.href = './login.html';
	      } else {

	          CookieUtil.unset("STOKEN", "/", null);
	      }
	}
	
 }

 function checkdate(cookiedate) {

	    var date = new Date(),
	      timestamp, newDate;

	    timestamp = date.getTime();

	    newDate = new Date(timestamp - 7 * 24 * 3600 * 1000);

	    var cookie_Date = new Date(cookiedate);

	    if (cookie_Date.getTime() > newDate.getTime()) {

	      return true;
	    }

	    return false;

	  }
	</script>

var StrutsUtils = {};

// gets an object with validation errors from string returned by 
// the ajaxValidation interceptor
StrutsUtils.getValidationErrors = function(data) {
    if (typeof data === "object") {
        return data;
    }
    else {
        if (data.indexOf("/* {") === 0) {
            return eval("( " + data.substring(2, data.length - 2) + " )");
        } else {
            return null;
        }
    }
};

StrutsUtils.clearValidationErrors = function(form) {
    var firstNode = StrutsUtils.firstElement(form);
    var xhtml = firstNode.tagName.toLowerCase() === "table";

    if(xhtml) {
        clearErrorMessagesXHTML(form);
        clearErrorLabelsXHTML(form);
    } else {
        clearErrorMessagesCSS(form);
        clearErrorLabelsCSS(form);
    }

    //clear previous global error messages
	if(StrutsUtils.errorLists[form] && StrutsUtils.errorLists[form] !== null) {
		form.parentNode.removeChild(StrutsUtils.errorLists[form]);
		StrutsUtils.errorLists[form] = null;
	}

};

StrutsUtils.errorLists = [];

// shows validation errors using functions from xhtml/validation.js
// or css_xhtml/validation.js
StrutsUtils.showValidationErrors = function(form, errors) {
    StrutsUtils.clearValidationErrors(form, errors);

	if (errors.errors) {
		var l, errorList = document.createElement("ul");

		errorList.setAttribute("class", "errorMessage");
		errorList.setAttribute("className", "errorMessage"); // ie hack cause ie does not support setAttribute

		for ( l = 0; l < errors.errors.length; l++) {
			var item = document.createElement("li");
			var itemText = document.createTextNode(errors.errors[l]);
			item.appendChild(itemText);

			errorList.appendChild(item);
		}
		
		form.parentNode.insertBefore(errorList, form);
		StrutsUtils.errorLists[form] = errorList;
	}

  var i, fieldName, firstNode = StrutsUtils.firstElement(form);
  var xhtml = firstNode.tagName.toLowerCase() === "table";
  if(errors.fieldErrors) {
    for(fieldName in errors.fieldErrors) {
      if(errors.fieldErrors.hasOwnProperty(fieldName)) {
        for(i = 0; i < errors.fieldErrors[fieldName].length; i++) {
          if(xhtml) {
            addErrorXHTML(form.elements[fieldName], errors.fieldErrors[fieldName][i]);
          } else {
            addErrorCSS(form.elements[fieldName], errors.fieldErrors[fieldName][i]);
          }
        }
      }
    }
  }
};

StrutsUtils.firstElement  = function(parentNode, tagName) {
  var node = parentNode.firstChild;
  while(node && node.nodeType !== 1){
    node = node.nextSibling;
  }
  if(tagName && node && node.tagName && node.tagName.toLowerCase() !== tagName.toLowerCase()) {
    node = StrutsUtils.nextElement(node, tagName);
  }
  return node;  
};

StrutsUtils.nextElement = function(node, tagName) {
  if(!node) { return null; }
  do {
    node = node.nextSibling;
  } while(node && node.nodeType !== 1);

  if(node && tagName && tagName.toLowerCase() !== node.tagName.toLowerCase()) {
    return StrutsUtils.nextElement(node, tagName);
  }
  return node;  
};

StrutsUtils.previousElement = function(node, tagName) {
  if(!node) { return null; }
  if(tagName) { tagName = tagName.toLowerCase(); }
  do {
    node = node.previousSibling;
  } while(node && node.nodeType !== 1);
  
  if(node && tagName && tagName.toLowerCase() !== node.tagName.toLowerCase()) {
    return StrutsUtils.previousElement(node, tagName);
  }
  return node;  
};

StrutsUtils.addOnLoad = function(func) {
  var oldonload = window.onload;
  if (typeof window.onload !== 'function') {
    window.onload = func;
  } else {
    window.onload = function() {
      oldonload();
      func();
    };
  }
};

StrutsUtils.addEventListener = function(element, name, observer, capture) {
  if (element.addEventListener) {
    element.addEventListener(name, observer, false);
  } else if (element.attachEvent) {
    element.attachEvent('on' + name, observer);
  }
};

 	searchAutoComplete:function(inputId,url,selectFunction){
 	$('#'+inputId).autocomplete({
  source: function(request, response) {
 	$.ajax({
  url: url,
  dataType: "json",
         data: {

	<script type="text/javascript">

 var IE6 = !-[1,] && !window.XMLHttpRequest;
var IE7=navigator.appName == "Microsoft Internet Explorer" && navigator.appVersion.match(/7./i)=='7.';
var nav=document.getElementById("divheader");
if(nav != null){
	navstyle = nav.style;
	if(!IE6 && !IE7)
	{
 navstyle.width="100%";
 navstyle.position="fixed";
 navstyle.top = "0px";
	}
	else if(IE6)
	{
 navstyle.position="absolute";
 navstyle.left="0";
 navstyle.top="0";
	}
	else if(IE7)
	{
 navstyle.width="100%";
 navstyle.left="0";
 navstyle.position="fixed";
 navstyle.top="0px";
	}
}
 function repairFloatStyle(currentNodeId,right,top) {
	var IE6 = !- [ 1, ] && !window.XMLHttpRequest;
	var IE7 = navigator.appName == "Microsoft Internet Explorer"
	&& navigator.appVersion.match(/7./i) == '7.';
	var currentNode = document.getElementById(currentNodeId); 
	if (typeof (currentNode) != "undefined" && currentNode!=null) {
 if (IE6) {
	var parentNode = currentNode.parentNode;
	if (typeof (parentNode) != "undefined" && parentNode!=null) {
 parentNode.style.position = "relative";
 currentNode.style.position = "absolute";
 currentNode.style.right = right;
 currentNode.style.top = top;
	}
 }
	}
}
</script>

	<script type="text/javascript">
	$(function(){
 $("#selectAcademic").bind("mouseover", function() {
	$("#tool_List").show();
	$('#triangle_down').removeClass().addClass('hover-up');
 }).bind("mouseout", function() {
	$("#tool_List").hide();
	$('#triangle_down').removeClass().addClass('hover-down');
 });
 $("#tool_List").hover(function(){
	$("#tool_List").toggle();
 });
 
 $("#selectDynamic").bind("mouseover", function() {
	$("#dynamic_List").show();
	$('#dynamic_down').removeClass().addClass('hover-up');
 }).bind("mouseout", function() {
	$("#dynamic_List").hide();
	$('#dynamic_down').removeClass().addClass('hover-down');
 });
 $("#dynamic_List").hover(function(){
	$("#dynamic_List").toggle();
 });

 var fq = getQueryString("fq");
 if (fq==null || fq == 0) { 
	changeDynamicType(0);
 } else if (fq == 1) {
	changeDynamicType(1);
 } else if (fq == 2) {
	changeDynamicType(2);
 } else if (fq == 3) {
	changeDynamicType(3);
 } else if (fq == 4) {
	changeDynamicType(4);
 } else if (fq == 5) {
	changeDynamicType(5);
 }
 
 getRealPath();
 if (!!window.ActiveXObject || "ActiveXObject" in window ||(navigator.userAgent.indexOf('MSIE') >= 0) 
	  && (navigator.userAgent.indexOf('Opera') < 0)) {
	    $("#search_block_Img").css("marginTop","-1px");
	  }; //判断是否IE浏览器
	});
	function changeSearch(searchType){
 if(searchType==1){
	document.getElementById("search_flag").innerHTML="站内";
	$("#tool_List").hide();
	$("#search_type").css('display','block');
	$("#ui-display").attr("value", "1");
	$(".sort").css("display", "inline-block");
 }else if(searchType==0){
	document.getElementById("search_flag").innerHTML="站外";
	$("#tool_List").hide();
	$("#search_type").css('display','none');
	$("#ui-display").attr("value", "0");
	$(".sort").hide();
 }
	}
	function changeDynamicType(searchDynamicType){
 if(searchDynamicType==0){
	document.getElementById("dynamic_flag").innerHTML="全部";
	$("#dynamic-display").css({"width":"60px","padding-left":"12px"});
	$("#dynamic_down").css("left","50px");
	$("#dynamic_List").hide();
	$("input[name^='searchMsgType']").val("0");
 }else if(searchDynamicType==1){
	document.getElementById("dynamic_flag").innerHTML="学者动态";
	$("#dynamic-display").css({"width":"70px","padding-left":"2px"});
	$("#dynamic_down").css("left","60px");
	$("#dynamic_List").hide();
	$("input[name^='searchMsgType']").val("1");
 }else if(searchDynamicType==2){
	document.getElementById("dynamic_flag").innerHTML="团队动态";
	$("#dynamic-display").css({"width":"70px","padding-left":"2px"});
	$("#dynamic_down").css("left","60px");
	$("#dynamic_List").hide();
	$("input[name^='searchMsgType']").val("2");
 }else if(searchDynamicType==3){
	document.getElementById("dynamic_flag").innerHTML="会议征文";
	$("#dynamic-display").css({"width":"70px","padding-left":"2px"});
	$("#dynamic_down").css("left","60px");
	$("#dynamic_List").hide();
	$("input[name^='searchMsgType']").val("3");
 }else if(searchDynamicType==4){
	document.getElementById("dynamic_flag").innerHTML="招聘招生";
	$("#dynamic-display").css({"width":"70px","padding-left":"2px"});
	$("#dynamic_down").css("left","60px");
	$("#dynamic_List").hide();
	$("input[name^='searchMsgType']").val("4");
 }else if(searchDynamicType==5){
	document.getElementById("dynamic_flag").innerHTML="学术快讯";
	$("#dynamic-display").css({"width":"70px","padding-left":"2px"});
	$("#dynamic_down").css("left","60px");
	$("#dynamic_List").hide();
	$("input[name^='searchMsgType']").val("5");
 }
	}
	function getRealPath(){
 var pathName=window.document.location.pathname;
	  var a_length = document.getElementById("search_Tabs").getElementsByTagName("a").length;
 if(pathName.indexOf("postMsgSearch.html") > 0 || pathName.indexOf("portalPostMsgSearchS.html") > 0){
	$("#search_logo").attr('src',"/images/scholat_dynamic.png");
	$("#selectDynamic").css('display','block');
	$("#search_type").css('display','none');
	$("#dynamic_type input[value=all]").attr("checked","checked");
   for(var i=0;i<a_length;i++){
 document.getElementById("search_Tabs").getElementsByTagName("a")[i].className = '';
   }
   document.getElementById("search_Tabs").getElementsByTagName("a")[0].className = 'cur';
 }else if(pathName.indexOf("papersearch.jsp") > 0){
	$("#search_logo").attr('src',"/images/scholat_paper.png");
	$("#selectDynamic").css('display','none');
	$("#selectAcademic").css('display','inline-block');
	$("#search_type input[value=Paper]").attr("checked","checked");
	var flag = request("isInsideSearch");
	if(flag == '1'){
 $("#search_type").css('display','block');
	}
   for(var i=0;i<a_length;i++){
 document.getElementById("search_Tabs").getElementsByTagName("a")[i].className = '';
   }
   document.getElementById("search_Tabs").getElementsByTagName("a")[1].className = 'cur';
 }else if(pathName.indexOf("portalSearchScholar.html") > 0 || pathName.indexOf("portalSearchScholarS.html") > 0){
	$("#search_logo").attr('src',"/images/scholat_scholar.png");
	$("#selectDynamic").css('display','none');
	$("#search_type").css('display','none');
   for(var i=0;i<a_length;i++){
 document.getElementById("search_Tabs").getElementsByTagName("a")[i].className = '';
   }
   document.getElementById("search_Tabs").getElementsByTagName("a")[2].className = 'cur';
 }else if(pathName.indexOf("portalSearchTeam.html") > 0 || pathName.indexOf("portalSearchTeamS.html") > 0){
	$("#search_logo").attr('src',"/images/scholat_team.png");
	$("#selectDynamic").css('display','none');
	$("#search_type").css('display','none');
   for(var i=0;i<a_length;i++){
 document.getElementById("search_Tabs").getElementsByTagName("a")[i].className = '';
   }
   document.getElementById("search_Tabs").getElementsByTagName("a")[3].className = 'cur';
 }else if(pathName.indexOf("portalSearchCourse.html") > 0 || pathName.indexOf("portalCourseSearchS.html") > 0){
	$("#search_logo").attr('src',"/images/scholat_course.png");
	$("#selectDynamic").css('display','none');
	$("#search_type").css('display','none');
   for(var i=0;i<a_length;i++){
 document.getElementById("search_Tabs").getElementsByTagName("a")[i].className = '';
   }
   document.getElementById("search_Tabs").getElementsByTagName("a")[4].className = 'cur';
 }
	}
	function clickTagA(tag, num) {
 var searchContent = $.trim($("#search_InputContent").val());
 if(num==1){//动态搜索
	if(searchContent != ""){
  var url = "portalPostMsgSearchS.html?q=" + searchContent + "&fq=0&orderType=0";
  $(tag).attr("href",encodeURI(basePath+url) );
	}
	else{
 $(tag).attr("href", basePath+"postMsgSearch.html");
	}
 }else if(num==2){//学术搜索
	if(searchContent==""){
 searchContent="*:*";
	}
	$(tag).attr("href",encodeURI(basePath+"search/papersearch.jsp?q="+searchContent));
 }else if(num==3){//学者搜索
	if(searchContent != ""){
 $(tag).attr( "href",encodeURI(basePath+"portalSearchScholarS.html?q=" + searchContent) );
	}
	else{
 $(tag).attr("href", basePath+"portalSearchScholar.html");
	}
 }else if(num==4){//团队搜索
	if (searchContent != "") {
 $(tag).attr("href",encodeURI( basePath+"portalSearchTeamS.html?q="+ searchContent + "&orderType=0" ));
	} else {
 $(tag).attr("href", basePath+"portalSearchTeam.html");
	}
 }else if(num==5){//课程搜索
	if (searchContent != "") {
 $(tag).attr("href", encodeURI(basePath+"portalCourseSearchS.html?q=" + searchContent+"&orderType=0")); //新版
	} else {
 $(tag).attr("href", basePath+"portalSearchCourse.html");
	}
 }
	}
</script>

window.onscroll=function()
{
	var docEle=document.documentElement;
	var st = docEle.scrollTop==0?document.body.scrollTop:docEle.scrollTop;
	var toTop = $("#toTop");
	if(st<60)
	{
	toTop.css("visibility", "hidden");
	}
	else
	{
 toTop.css("visibility", "visible");
	}
}

 <script type="text/javascript">
	  function leaveMessageConfirm(){
	   if (window.confirm("留言需要先登录!"))
	     window.location.href="scholarLeaveMessage.html?Entry=lqlz";
	  }
 $(document).ready(function(){	
   
   repairFloatStyle('search_block_Img',"0px","25px"); 
	$("#search_InputContent").click(function(){changeSubType(1);});
	var q = getUrlParameter("q"); 
	$("#search_InputContent").val(q);
	$("#search_InputContent").click(function(){submitType=1});
	var orderType = getQueryString("orderType");
	if (orderType==null || orderType == 0) {
 var orderDiv = document.getElementById("sortTypeCombine");
 if(orderDiv!=null)
 	orderDiv.checked = true;
	} else if (orderType == 1) {
 var orderDiv = document.getElementById("sortTypeHits");
 if(orderDiv!=null)
 	orderDiv.checked = true;
	}
 });
 $(function() {
	var $div_li = $("div.tab_menu ul li");
	$div_li.click(function() {
 $(this).addClass("selected").siblings().removeClass("selected");
 var index = $div_li.index(this)+1;
 $('#typeid').attr('value', index);
 $('#search_InputContent').focus();
 if(index==5)
 	setType('Conference');
 else if(index==6)
 	setType('Journal');
 else 
 	setType('');
	}).hover(function() {$(this).addClass("hover");	}, 
		function() {$(this).removeClass("hover");}
	);
 });
 
 var searchType=2; 
 function selectTab(id){
	searchType=id;	
	for(var i=1; i<=12; i++){
 if(i==id){
 	$("#st"+i).addClass("cur");
 }else{
 	$("#st"+i).removeClass("cur");
 }
	}
	if(id==4)
 setType('Conference');
	else if(id==5)
 setType('Journal');
	else
 setType('');
	$("#search_InputContent").focus();	
 }
 
 function advancedsearch_portal(){
	var location = window.location.href;
	if(location.indexOf("search") > 0)
 window.location.href = "advancedsearch.jsp?typeid="+searchType;
	else
 window.location.href = "search/advancedsearch.jsp?typeid="+searchType;
 }
 
 var submitType=1;
 function changeSubType(type){
	submitType=type;	
 }
 
 function BindEnter(obj){	
   
   if(obj!=null&&(obj.keyCode == 13||obj.which==13)){	   
	  subForm(0);
   }
 }
 function subForm(orderType) {
	var searchContent = $.trim($("#search_InputContent").val());
	if(searchContent != ""){
 window.location.href = "portalSearchScholarS.html?q=" + encodeURI(searchContent) 
 + "&orderType=" + orderType;;
	}
	else{
 window.location.href = "portalSearchScholar.html";
	}
 }
 function setType(t) {
	var querybox=$('#search_InputContent')[0];
	var v;
	if(t!=''){
 if (querybox.value.indexOf('type:') >= 0)
 	v=querybox.value.replace(/type:[a-zA-Z]+/g, "type:"+t);
 else
 	v="type:" + t + " " + querybox.value;
	}
	else{
 v=querybox.value.replace(/type:[a-zA-Z]+/g, '').replace(/(^\s+)|(\s+$)/g,'');
	}
	querybox.value=v;
 }
 function printDate(){
	var dateString;
	var curDay = new Date();
	var month = curDay.getMonth()+ 1
	dateString = curDay.getFullYear()+"年"+month+"月"+curDay.getDate()+"日 "+'星期'+'日一二三四五六'.charAt(curDay.getDay()); 
	document.write(dateString);	
 }
 
 function card_out(n,t,obj,q){
	var picTop = $(obj).offset().top;
	var picLeft = $(obj).offset().left;
	var top = picTop;
	var left = picLeft;
	var bodyWidth = $(document.body).width();
	var bodyHeight = $(document.body).height();
	if(q==1)
	{	if(picLeft+250>bodyWidth){
 	left = picLeft-150;
 	left_j = 1;
 }else{
 	left = picLeft+20;
 }
 if(picTop-170<0){
 	top = picTop+80;
 	top_j = 1;
 }else{
 	top = picTop-110;
 }
	}
	if(t==1){	
 clearTimeout(timeoutID2);
 $("#mp"+n).removeClass();
 if(left_j==0&&top_j==0)
 	{
  $("#mp"+n).addClass("mp_scholar_l");
  $("#mp"+n).css({"left":left+"px","top":top+"px"});
 	}
 else if(left_j==0&&top_j==1)
 	{
  $("#mp"+n).addClass("mp_scholar_l_d");
  $("#mp"+n).css({"left":left+"px","top":top+"px"});
 	}
 else if(left_j==1&&top_j==0)
 	{
  $("#mp"+n).addClass("mp_scholar_r");
  $("#mp"+n).css({"left":left+"px","top":top+"px"});
 	}
 else if(left_j==1&&top_j==1)
 	{
  $("#mp"+n).addClass("mp_scholar_r_d");
  $("#mp"+n).css({"left":left+"px","top":top+"px"});
 	}
	}
	else if(t==2){ 
 timeoutID2=setTimeout(function(){$("#mp"+n).removeClass(); $("#mp"+n).addClass("hidden");top_j = 0;left_j = 0;},200);
 }
 }
 
 function card_delay(n,t,obj,q)
 {
	if(t==1)
	{
   timeoutID1 = setTimeout(function(){card_out(n,t,obj,q)},500);
   }
   if(t==2)
	{
  	clearTimeout(timeoutID1);	
  	card_out(n,t,obj,q);
   }
 }
 </script>
</html>

/**

var selpapercount=1;//缂虹涓绔
function selecttype(type)
{
	var keyword=($('#searchGroupInput').val().replace(/[ ]type:\\*|[ ]type:JournalPaper|[ ]type:ConferencePaper|[ ]type:Book|[ ]type:Thesis|[ ]type:InCollection|[ ]type:Unknown|[ ]type:Conference|[ ]type:Journal|[ ]type:BookChapter|[ ]type:Reference/g,""));
	//keyword=keyword.replace(/[ ]/g,"");
	$('#searchGroupInput').attr('value',keyword+' type:'+type);
	curPage=1;
	submitForm(); 
}
String.prototype.trim =function() 
{
	return this.replace(/^\\s+|\\s+$/g, "");
}

function addyearlist(year,num)
{
	if(year.length!=4)
		return;
	
	var str="<li><a href='#' onclick='selectyear("+year+")'>"+year+"</a><span class='number'>("+num+")</span></li>";
	$('#yearlist').append(str);
}
function addyearlistmore(year,num)
{
	if(year.length!=4)
		return;
	
	var str="<li><a href='#' onclick='selectyear("+year+")'>"+year+"</a><span class='number'>("+num+")</span></li>";
	$('#yearlistmore').append(str);
}

function autoaddyeallist()
{
	var myDate = new Date(); 
	var year=myDate.getYear();
	   
	for(var i=0;i<20;i++)
	{
	year=year-i;
	var str="<li id='year"+year+"'><a href='#' onclick='selectyear("+year+")'>"+year+"</a></li>";
	$('#yearlist').append(str);
	}
}

function selectyear(year)
{
	curPage=1;
	var keyword=($('#searchGroupInput').val().replace(/[ ]year:\\*|[ ]year:(\\d){4}/g,""));
	var keyword=(keyword.replace(/[ ]year:(\\[).*(\\])/g,""));
	$('#searchGroupInput').attr('value',keyword+' year:'+year);
	submitForm(); 
}

function showdivyeardomain()
{
	$('#divyeardomain').show();
	$('#startyear').focus();
}


function showdivabstract(id)
{
	$('#divabstract'+id).show();
	$('#divhideabstract'+id).show();
	$('#divshowabstract'+id).hide();
}

function hidedivabstract(id)
{
	$('#divabstract'+id).hide();
	$('#divhideabstract'+id).hide();
	$('#divshowabstract'+id).show();
}

function confirmyeardomain()
{
	if ($('#startyear').val()=='') return;
	if ($('#endyear').val()=='') return;
	curPage=1;
	var keyword=($('#searchGroupInput').val().replace(/[ ]year:\\*|[ ]year:(\\d){4}/g,""));
	var keyword=(keyword.replace(/[ ]year:(\\[).*(\\])/g,""));
	
	$('#searchGroupInput').attr('value',keyword+' year:['+$('#startyear').val()+' '+$('#endyear').val()+']');
	submitForm();
}

function searchmypaper()
{
	if ($("#username").val()=='')
	{
	     alert("璇峰诲");
	     location.href="../login.html";   
	}
	else
	{
		 var username=$("#username").val();
		 var work_unit=$("#workunit").val();
		 if (work_unit=="") work_unit="*";
		 var strquery='author_exact:'+username+' organization:'+work_unit;
		 //var strquery='author_exact:'+username;
		$('#searchGroupInput').attr('value',strquery);
		curPage=1;
		submitForm(); 
	}
}

function getcollectsnum() //峰惰绔\xB0
{
	if ($("#username").val()=='') 
	{
		 $("#inputcollectnum").attr('value','');
		 return false;
	}
	$.ajax(
	{
		  type: "post",
		  url: "collectpaperlist_num.html", 
		  timeout:60000,
		  dataType: "text",
		  success:function(data)
		  {
			  $("#inputcollectnum").attr('value','('+data+')');
		  },
		  error:function()
		  {
			  $("#inputcollectnum").attr('value','');
	      }
   });
}

function getsavepapersnum() //峰淇瀛绔
{
	if ($("#username").val()=='') 
	{
		$("#inputsavepapernum").attr('value','');
		return false;
	}
	$.ajax(
	{
		  type: "post",
		  url: "savepaperlist_num.html", 
		  timeout:60000,
		  dataType: "text",
		  success:function(data){
		  //alert(data);
		  $("#inputsavepapernum").attr('value','('+data+')');
		           
		  },
		  error:function(){
 
		  $("#inputsavepapernum").attr('value','');
	      }
	});
}

function CheckedAll()
{ 
	$(':checkbox').attr('checked','checked'); 
} 
function CheckedNo()
{ 
	$(':checkbox').attr('checked',''); 
} 

function CollectAll()
{
	var arr = $(':checkbox:checked');
	selpapercount=arr.length;
	if (arr.length==0) 
		alert("\x80╀换浣绔!"); 
	if (arr.length>1)
		var r=confirm("纭璁ゆ惰\x80璁烘?");
	if (r==false)
		return;
	for(var i=0;i<arr.length;i++)
	  collectpaper(arr[i].value); 
	selpapercount=1; 
}
function SaveAll()
{
	var arr = $(':checkbox:checked');
	selpapercount=arr.length;
	if (arr.length==0) 
		alert("\x80╀换浣绔!"); 

	if (arr.length>1)
		var r=confirm("纭璁や瀛\x80璁烘?");
	if (r==false)
		return;
   
	for(var i=0;i<arr.length;i++) 
	  savepaper(arr[i].value); 
	selpapercount=1; 
}



function IgnoreAll()
{
	var arr = $(':checkbox:checked');
	selpapercount=arr.length;
	if (arr.length==0) 
		alert("\x80╀换浣绔!"); 
	if (arr.length>=1)
		var r=confirm("蹇界ョ绔灏涓ㄨㄨ\x90,纭璁よユ浣?");
	if (r==false)
	   return;
	for(var i=0;i<arr.length;i++)
		savepaperIDignored(arr[i].value); 
	selpapercount=1; 
}

function advanceconfirm()
{
	//-------版
	var strquery='';
	var val;
	if((val=$('#A_title').val())!='')
	    strquery+='title:'+val;
	
	if((val=$('#A_authors').val())!='')
	      strquery+=' author_exact:'+val;
	
	if((val=$('#A_organization').val())!='')
	      strquery+=' organization:'+val;
	
	if((val=$('#A_keyword').val())!='')
	      strquery+=' keyword:'+val;
	
	if((val=$('#A_source').val())!='')
	      strquery+=' source:'+val;
	
	if((val=$('#A_year').val())!='')
	{
		var pos=val.indexOf('-');
		if(pos>=0)
		{
			var yearFrom=val.substring(0,pos).trim();
			var yearTo=val.substring(pos+1).trim();
			if(yearFrom=='') yearFrom='*';
			if(yearTo=='') yearTo='*';
			strquery+=' year:['+yearFrom+' TO '+yearTo+']';
		}
		else
			strquery+=' year:'+val;
	}
	rows=$('#listcount').val();
	
	if (strquery=='')  
		return false;
	 window.location.href="papersearch.jsp?q="+$.trim(strquery)+"&rows="+rows;  
}

	});

	{
	   $(this).attr('value','')
	});

	$("input[name=A_source]").each(function()
	{
	   $(this).attr('value','')
	});
}

function advanceconfirm_scholar()
{
	//-------版
	var strquery='';
	$("input[name=scholarChineseName]").each(function(){
	    if ($(this).attr("value")!='') 
	    {
	      strquery+='title:'+$(this).attr("value");
	    }
	 });
 
	$("input[name=scholarEnglishName]").each(function(){
	    if ($(this).attr("value")!='') 
	    {
	      strquery+='title:'+$(this).attr("value");
	    }
	 }); 
 
	 $("input[name=scholarUnit]").each(function(){
	    if ($(this).attr("value")!='') 
	    {
	      strquery+='title:'+$(this).attr("value");
	    }
	 });

	 $("input[name=scholarField]").each(function(){
	    if ($(this).attr("value")!='') 
	    {
	      strquery+='title:'+$(this).attr("value");
	    }
	 });
	 if ((strquery.replace(/[ ]/g,""))=="") return false;

	$("form[name=portalsiteScholarAdvanceSearch_scholar]").each(function(){
 
	   $(this).submit();
	 });
}

function getDesc(doc)
{
	var str="";
	if(doc.author!=null)
		str=doc.author+','+'. ';
	str+=doc.title+". ";
	if(doc.source==null)
		doc.source='unknown source';
	str+=doc.source+","+doc.year;
	if(doc.vol!=null)
		str+=","+doc.vol;
	if(doc.issue!=null)
		str+="("+doc.issue+")";
	if(doc.pages!=null)
		str+=":"+doc.pages;
	return str;
}

function showItem(doc,index,detail){
	var html='<div class="divItem" id="divItem'+index+'">';
	
	if(!detail){
		html+=generateDocTools(doc,index);
		if(doc.type == 'Reference'){
			
			html+='<div class="itemTitle"><span>'+highlight(doc.citation)+'</span></div>';
			
		}else{
			html+='<div class="itemTitle"><span>'+highlight(doc.title)+'</span></div>';
			
			
		}
		
	}
	else{
		if(doc.type == 'Reference'){
			//var index = doc.timestamp.toString().indexOf('T');
			//var date = doc.timestamp.toString().substring(0,index);
			html+='<div class="itemTitle"><span>'+highlight(doc.citation)+'</span></div>';
			//html += '<div class="itemType" style="margin-left:50px;">ユ锛\x9A'+ date +'<div>';
		}else{
			
			html+='<div class="itemTitle"><span>'+highlight(doc.title)+'</span></div>';
		}
		//html+='<div class="itemTitle">'+doc.title+'</div>';
		
	}
	
	if(doc.type=='JournalPaper'||doc.type=='ConferencePaper'||doc.type=='Unknown'){
		if(doc.abstract){
				html+='<div id="itemAbstract" class="itemAbstract"><strong>瑕锛\x9A&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong>';
				if(doc.abstract.length>230)
					html+=highlight(doc.abstract.substring(0,227))+'...<span class="itemAbstractSwitch" onclick="switchAbstract(this.parentElement,'+index+',true)">More&nbsp;禄</span>';
				else
					html+=highlight(doc.abstract);
				html+='</div>';
	
		}
		
		html+='<div class="itemAuthor"><strong class="itemName">浣\x80锛</strong><div class="itemContent">'+getAuthors(doc)+'&nbsp;</div></div>';
		if(doc.type=='JournalPaper')
			html+='<div class="itemType"><strong class="itemName">绫诲锛\x9A</strong><div class="itemContent">璁烘</div></div>';
		else if(doc.type=='ConferencePaper')
			html+='<div class="itemType"><strong class="itemName">绫诲锛\x9A</strong><div class="itemContent">浼璁璁烘</div></div>';
		else if(doc.type=='Unknown')
			html+='<div class="itemType"><strong class="itemName">绫诲锛\x9A</strong><div class="itemContent"></div></div>';
		
		if(doc.source||doc["journal-ref"])
		     html+='<div class="itemSource"><strong class="itemName">ユ锛\x9A</strong><div class="itemContent">'+getSource(doc)+'&nbsp;</div></div>';
		if(doc.organization)
			html+='<div class="itemOrganization"><strong class="itemName">浣\x80浣锛</strong><div class="itemContent">'+highlight(doc.organization)+'</div></div>';
		if(doc.keyword){
			var keyword = getKeywords(doc);
			if(keyword.length>0)
				html+='<div class="itemKeywords"><strong class="itemName">抽璇锛</strong><div class="itemContent">'+keyword+'&nbsp;</div></div>';
		}
		if(doc.comments)
			html+='<div><strong class="itemName">澶娉锛\x9A</strong><div class="itemContent">'+doc.comments+'&nbsp;</div></div>';
	
	}
	else if(doc.type=='Book' || doc.type=='BookChapter'){
		//浣\x80淇℃\xAF
		html+='<div class="itemAuthor"><strong class="itemName">浣\x80锛</strong><div class="itemContent">'+getAuthors(doc)+'&nbsp;</div>';
		
		if(doc.author_affiliation){
			html += '<strong class="itemName">浣\x80浣锛</strong><div class="itemContent">'+doc.author_affiliation+'</div>';
		}
		if(detail){
			if(doc.author_email)
				html += '<strong class="itemName">浣\x80绠憋</strong><div class="itemContent">'+doc.author_email+'</div>';
		}
			
		html+='</div>';
 
		var type='';
		if(doc.type=='Book')
			type='瀛涓';
		else
			type='句功绔';
		html += '<div class="itemType"><strong class="itemName">绫诲锛\x9A</strong><div class="itemContent">'+type+'</div>';

		if(doc.booktitle)
			html+='<strong class="itemName">句功绉帮\x9A</strong><div class="itemContent">'+doc.booktitle+'</div>';

		html+='<div class="itemSource">';
		if(doc.publisher)
		     html+='<strong class="itemName">虹绀撅</strong><div class="itemContent">'+highlight(doc.publisher);
		//ュ勾
		if(doc.year){
			html+='&nbsp;'+doc.year+"骞\xB4";
			if(doc.month)
				html+=doc.month+"\x88";
			html+="虹";
		}
		if(doc.pages)
			html+=",&nbsp;椤电锛\x9A"+doc.pages;
		html+='&nbsp;</div></div>';

		if(doc.isbn)
			html+='<div class="itemFields"><strong>ISBN锛\x9A</strong>'+doc.isbn+'</div>';
		if(doc.img)
			html+='<div class="itemImg"><img src="'+doc.img+'"></div>';
		
		//濡璁烘缁椤靛氨灞绀烘村瀹\xB9
		if(detail){
			html+='<div class="itemMoreDetail">';
			
			if(doc.abstract){
				html+='<div id="itemAbstract" class="itemAbstract"><strong >瑕锛\x9A&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong>';
				if(doc.abstract.length>230)
					html+=highlight(doc.abstract.substring(0,227))+'...<span class="itemAbstractSwitch" onclick="switchAbstract(this.parentElement,'+index+',true)">More&nbsp;禄</span>';
				else
					html+=highlight(doc.abstract);
				html+='</div>';
	
		    }
			if(doc.doi)
				html+='<strong class="itemName">DOI锛\x9A</strong><div class="itemContent">'+doc.doi+'</div>';
			if(doc.print_isbn)
				html+='<strong class="itemName">Print ISBN锛\x9A</strong><div class="itemContent">'+doc.print_isbn+'</div>';
			if(doc.online_isbn)
				html+='<strong class="itemName">Online ISBN锛\x9A</strong><div class="itemContent">'+doc.online_isbn+'</div>';
			
			html+='</div">';
		}

	}
	else if(doc.type=='Journal'){
		html+='<div class="itemType"><strong>绫诲锛\x9A</strong></div>';
	}
	else if(doc.type=='Conference'){
		html+='<div class="itemType"><strong>绫诲锛\x9A</strong>浼璁</div>';
		if(doc.author&&doc.author.length>0){
			html+='<div class="itemAuthor"><strong class="itemName">涓荤锛\x9A</strong><div class="itemContent">'+getAuthors(doc)+"&nbsp;</div></div>";
		}
		if(doc.series){
			html+='<div>Series锛\x9A'+doc.series;
			if(doc.year)
				html+=', '+doc.year;
			if(doc.vol)
				html+=' ('+doc.vol+')';
			html+="</div>";
		}
		if(doc.publisher){
			html+='<div><strong>虹绀撅</strong>'+doc.publisher;
			html+='</div>';
		}
		if(doc.isbn)
			html+='<div><strong>ISBN锛\x9A</strong>'+doc.isbn+'</div>';
		
				
		if(doc.subject)
			html+='<div><strong>涓婚锛\x9A</strong>'+doc.subject+"</div>";
		if(doc.location)
			html+='<div><strong>浼璁扮癸\x9A</strong>'+doc.location+'</div>';
		if(doc.startdate){
			html+='<div><strong>浼璁ユ锛\x9A</strong>'+doc.startdate.substring(0,10);
			if(doc.enddate)
				html+=' ~ '+doc.enddate.substring(0,10);
			html+="</div>";
		}
		if(doc.duedate)
			html+='<div><strong>绋挎ユ锛\x9A</strong>'+doc.duedate.substring(0,10)+"</div>";
		
	}
	else if(doc.type=='Thesis'){
		html+='<div classs="itemAuthor"><strong>浣\x80锛</strong>'+getAuthors(doc)+'</div>'
			+'<div class="itemType"><strong>绫诲锛\x9A</strong>';

		if(doc.degree=='doctor')
			html+='澹瀛浣璁烘';
		else if(doc.degree=='master')
			html+='纭澹瀛浣璁烘';
		else if(doc.degree=='postdoc')
			html+='澹虹ュ\x8A';
		else if(doc.degree=='undergraduate')
			html+='绉瀛浣璁烘';
		else 
			html+='瀛浣璁烘';

		if(doc.school)
			html+='<div class="itemOrganization"><strong>瀛★\x9A</strong>'+highlight(doc.school)+'</div>';
	}
	else if(doc.type=='InCollection'){
		html+='<div class="itemAuthor"><strong>浣\x80锛</strong>'+getAuthors(doc)+'</div>'
	     +'<div class="itemType"><strong>绫诲锛\x9A</strong>Book Chapter</div>';
	}
	
	
	html+="<div class='itemUrl'><strong>稿抽炬ワ\x9A</strong>";
	for(var i in doc.url)
	{	
		html+="<div style='padding-left:94px;'><a style='color: #3A6DDA;' " +
			"target='_blank' href='" + doc.url[i] + "'>" 
			+ doc.url[i] + "</a></div>";
	}
	html+="</div>";
	if(arguments[3]!== undefined&&arguments[3]!==null){//濡绗涓涓浼锛璇存showpdflist椤甸\xA2
		
		html+="<span>";
		html+="<a href='javascript:void(0)' onclick='showPaperContent(this,\\""+doc.id+"\\")' style='border:3px solid #399;padding:3px;margin-left:3px;'>璇</a>";
		html+="<a href='javascript:void(0);' onclick='showPrivilegeDialog(this,\\""+doc.id+"\\")' style='border:3px solid #399;padding:3px;margin-left:3px;' >淇规</a>";
		html+="<a href='javascript:void(0);' onclick='comfirmRemoveDialog(this,\\""+doc.id+"\\")' style='border:3px solid #399;padding:3px;margin-left:3px;'>や浼pdf</a>";
		html+='</span></div>';
		
		return html;
	}
	html+='</div>';
	return html;
}

function generateDocTools(doc,index){
	var html='<div class="itemTools">';
	html+='<span class="itemFav" title="惰" onclick=\\'collectpaper('+index+')\\'></span>';
	if(doc.type!='Conference'&&doc.type!='Journal'){
		html+='<span class="itemBibtex" title="峰BibTeX淇℃" onclick=\\'getBibtex('+index+',this);return false;\\'></span>';
	}
	var docId=doc.id;
	var docTitle=doc.title;
	
	
	//html+='<span class="itemRead" title="娴瑙绔" onclick=\\'showPaperContent(this,"'+docId+'");return false;\\'></span>';//淇class涓浜浠\xB6
	
	
	//html+='<span class="itemUpload" title="涓浼绔" onclick=\\'uploadPaperPdf(this,"'+docId+'","'+docTitle+'");return false;\\'></span>';
		
	html+='</div>';
	return html;
}
//濡paper涓杞介炬ワ冲ョ瀹
function showPaperContent(elem,id){
	
	var url="hasPaper.html";
	$.ajax({
		type:"post",
		url:"hasPaper.html",
		data:{paperid:id},
		datatype:"text",
		timeout:60000,
		success:function(data){
			if(window.ActiveXObject){
				
			}else if(data instanceof Document){//涓data涓document
				data=arguments[2].responseText;
			}
			if(data=='2'){
				$("#waitLayout").css("display","block");
				$("#waitDialog").css("display","block");
				location.href="paperContent.html?paperid="+id;
			}else if(data=='1'){
				alert("璇ヨ烘涓寮\x80鹃璇\xBB");
			}else{
				alert("舵病浜哄浜璇ヨ烘锛娌″娉璇伙\x81");
			}
		},
		error:function(){
			
		}
	});
	
	
	
}
function uploadPaperPdf(elem,id,title){
	
	$.ajax({
		type:"post",
		url:"hasPaper.html",
		data:{paperid:id},
		datatype:"text",
		timeout:60000,
		success:function(data){
			if(window.ActiveXObject){
				
			}else if(data instanceof Document){//涓data涓document
				data=arguments[2].responseText;
			}
			if(data=='0'){
				$("#uploadPaperPdfDialog").css("display","inline");
				$("#uploadPaperPdfId").attr("value",id);
				$("#uploadPaperPdfTitle").attr("value",title);
			}else if(data=='1'||data=='2'){
				//$("#showPaperContentDialog").css("display","inline");
				alert("宸茬ㄦ峰浜璇ユ绔浜锛");
			}
		},
		error:function(){
			
		}
	});
	
	
}

	var paperid=$("#removePaperId").val();
	location.href="removeUploadPaperPdf.html?paperid="+encodeURI(paperid);
}

}
function getBibtex2(index,e){
	var msg='';
	var status = true;
	var d;
	if(typeof(docs) == "undefined")
	{
		d = doc;
		status = false;
	}
	else
		d = docs[index];
 
	if(d.type=='JournalPaper'){
		msg+='@article{'+d.title+',\\n'
			+' author={'+d.author+'},\\n'
			+' title={'+d.title+'}';
		if(d.source)
			msg+=',\\n journal={'+d.source+'}';
		if(d.year)
			msg+=',\\n year={'+d.year+'}';
		if(d.vol)
			msg+=',\\n volume={'+d.vol+'}';
		if(d.issue)
			msg+=',\\n issue={'+d.issue+'}';
		if(d.pages)
			msg+=',\\n pages={'+d.pages+'}';
		if(d.doi)
			msg+=',\\n doi={'+d.doi+'}';
				
		msg+='\\n}';
	}
	else if(d.type=='ConferencePaper'){
		msg+='@inproceedings{'+d.title+',\\n'
			+'  author={'+d.author+'},\\n'
			+'  title={'+d.title+'}';
		if(d.source)
			msg+=',\\n booktitle={'+d.source+'}';
		if(d.year)
			msg+=',\\n year={'+d.year+'}';
		if(d.month)
			msg+=',\\n month={'+d.month+'}';
		if(d.pages)
			msg+=',\\n pages={'+d.pages+'}';
		if(d.doi)
			msg+=',\\n doi={'+d.doi+'}';
				
		msg+='\\n}';
	}
	else if(d.type=='Thesis'){
		if(d.degree=='master')
			msg+='@masterthesis{';
		else
			msg+='@phdthesis{';
			
		msg+=d.title+',\\n author={'+d.author[0]+'}'
			 +',\\n title={'+d.title+'}';
		
		if(d.school)
			msg+=',\\n school={'+d.school+'}';
		if(d.pages) 
			msg+=',\\n pages={'+d.pages+'}';
		if(d.year)
			msg+=',\\n year={'+d.year+'}';
		if(d.month)
			msg+=',\\n month={'+d.month+'}';
		msg+='\\n}';
	}
	else if(d.type=='InCollection' || d.type=='BookChapter'){
		msg='@incollection{'+d.title
			 +',\\n author={'+d.author+'}'
			 +',\\n title={'+d.title+'}';
 
		if(d.source)
			msg+=',\\n booktitle={'+d.source+'}';
		if(d.year)
			msg+=',\\n year={'+d.year+'}';
		if(d.month)
			msg+=',\\n month={'+d.month+'}';
		if(d.pages)
			msg+=',\\n pages={'+d.pages+'}';
		if(d.vol)
			msg+=',\\n volume={'+d.vol+'}';
		if(d.series)
			msg+=',\\n series={'+d.series+'}';
		msg+='\\n}';
	}
	else if(d.type=='Book'){
		msg='@book{'+d.title+',\\n'+
			'  author={'+d.author+'},\\n'
			+'  title={'+d.title+'}';
		if(d.publisher)
			msg+=',\\n publisher={'+d.publisher+'}';
		if(d.year)
			msg+=',\\n year={'+d.year+'}';
		if(d.month)
			msg+=',\\n month={'+d.month+'}';
		if(d.pages)
			msg+=',\\n pages={'+d.pages+'}';
		if(d.vol)
			msg+=',\\n volume={'+d.vol+'}';
		if(d.series)
			msg+=',\\n series={'+d.series+'}';
		msg+='\\n}';
	}
	if(msg=='')
		return;
	if(status==true) {
		$("#bibtex").val(msg);
		$('#txtBibtex')[0].value=msg;
		$('#divPopup').show();
		$('#divPopup')[0].style.top=(mousePos.y)+'px';
		$('#divPopup')[0].style.left=(mousePos.x-$('#divPopup')[0].offsetWidth-30)+'px';
	}
	else
		$("#bibtex").val(msg);
}
function getMousePoint(event) {
    var e = event || window.event;
    var scrollX = document.documentElement.scrollLeft || document.body.scrollLeft;
    var scrollY = document.documentElement.scrollTop || document.body.scrollTop;
    var x = e.pageX || e.clientX + scrollX;
    var y = e.pageY || e.clientY + scrollY;
    return { 'x': x, 'y': y };
}

function getAuthors(doc){
	var authors=doc.author||doc.editor;
	var str='';
	var list=[];

	if (doc.author != null) {
		var authors = doc.author;
		for ( var a in authors) {
			if (/.*[\\u4e00-\\u9fa5]+.*$/.test(authors[a]))
				list = list.concat(authors[a].split(/[,锛\x8C;锛\s]+/));
			else
				list.push(authors[a]);
		}
	} else if (doc.editor != null) {
		var authors = doc.editor;
		list = list.concat(authors.split(/[,锛]+/));
		 
	}	
	
	for(var a in list){
		str+='<a  style="color: #3A6DDA;" href=\\'papersearch.jsp?q=author:"'+list[a]+'"\\'>'+highlight(list[a])+'</a>,&nbsp;&nbsp;';
	}
	
	return str.substring(0,str.length-13);
}

function getSource(doc){
	var str="";
	if(doc.source)
		str+='<a style="color: #3A6DDA;" href=\\'papersearch.jsp?q=source:"'+doc.source+'"\\'>'+highlight(doc.source)+"</a>";
	else if(doc["journal-ref"])
		str+=doc["journal-ref"];
	else
		str+='undefined';
	if(doc.year)
		str+=',&nbsp;'+doc.year;
	if(doc.vol!=null)
		str+=','+doc.vol;
	if(doc.issue!=null)
		str+='('+doc.issue+')';
	if(doc.pages!=null)
		str+=":"+doc.pages;
	return str;
}

function switchAbstract(node,i,expand){
	var html;
	if(expand)
		html='<div class="itemAbstract">瑕锛\x9A'+highlight(docs[i].abstract)
			  	+'<span class="itemAbstractSwitch" onclick="switchAbstract(this.parentElement,'+i+',false)">Less&nbsp;芦</span></div>';
	else
		html='<div class="itemAbstract">瑕锛\x9A'+highlight(docs[i].abstract.substring(0,227))
				+'...<span class="itemAbstractSwitch" onclick="switchAbstract(this.parentElement,'+i+',true)">More&nbsp;禄</span>';
	
	node.innerHTML=html;
}

function getKeywords(doc){
	var str='';
	var len=doc.keyword.length;
	if(len>8)
		len=8;
	var count=0;
	for ( var kw in doc.keyword) {
		if (doc.keyword[kw].length > 0) {
			str += '<a style="color: #3A6DDA;" href=\\'papersearch.jsp?q=keyword:"'
					+ doc.keyword[kw]
					+ '"\\'>'
					+ highlight(doc.keyword[kw])
					+ '</a>锛\x9B&nbsp;';
			count = count + 1;
			if (count > len)
				break;
		}
	}
	return str;
}

function getUrls(doc){
	var urls;
	doc.url=doc.url.replace(/&amp;/g,'&');
	if(doc.url.indexOf('`')>=0)
		urls=doc.url.split('`');
	else if(doc.url.indexOf(';')>=0)
		urls=doc.url.split(';');
	else
		urls=[doc.url];
	
	var omit=/(^http:\\/\\/academic.research.microsoft.com|^http:\\/\\/www.cnki.com.cn)/
	for(var u=urls.length-1;u>=0;u--){
		if(urls[u]==''||omit.test(urls[u]))
			urls.splice(u, 1);
	}
	if(urls.length<=0)
		return '';
	
	var showUrl=0;
	for(var u=0;u<urls.length;u++){
		if(urls[u].substring(urls[u].lastIndexOf('.')+1)=='pdf'){
			showUrl=u;
		}
	}
	if(showUrl!=0){
		var t=urls[showUrl];
		urls[showUrl]=urls[0];
		urls[0]=t;
	}
	
	var str='<div class="itemUrl"><div><a style="color: #3A6DDA;" target="_blank"  href="'+urls[0]+'">'+urls[0]+"</a>";
	if(urls.length==1){
		str+='</div>';
	}
	else{
		str+='<span onclick="switchUrl(this)" class="moreUrls" title="村炬"></span></div>';
		for(var u=1;u<urls.length;u++){
			str+='<div class="itemMoreUrls"><a target="_blank" href="'+urls[u]+'">'+urls[u]+'</a></div>';
		}
	}
	str+='</div>';
	return str;
}

function switchUrl(e,show){
	var itemNode=e.parentElement.parentElement;
	if(e.className=='moreUrls'){
		itemNode.className='itemUrlAll';
		e.className='lessUrls';
		e.style.title='跺';
		//e.innerHTML='Less&nbsp;芦';
	}
	else{
		itemNode.className='itemUrl';
		e.className='moreUrls';
		e.style.title='村炬';
		//e.innerHTML='More&nbsp;禄';
	}
}

var page = $("#page");
page.empty();
for(var i=1;i<=max;i++) {
    var option = $("<option>").text("绗\xAC"+i+"椤\xB5").val(i);
    page.append(option);
}
page.val(current);    

}

page.empty();

}

//惰绔
function collectpaper(i)
{
 
 //峰璁烘稿充俊
 //var key =$("#I_desc"+i).val().replace(/[ ]/g,"").split(".");
 var item="#divItem"+i; 
 var authors=$(item+' .itemAuthor').text().substring(3);
 var title=docs[i].title;
 var source=$(item+' .itemSource').text().substring(3);
 var year=docs[i].year;
 var url =docs[i].url;
 var detail='';
 if(docs[i].keyword)
	 detail+=docs[i].keyword+'; '+"\\n\\n";
 if(docs[i].abstract)
	 detail+=docs[i].abstract;

  if(!confirm("纭璁ゆ惰濡涓璁烘\x97?"+"\\n棰:" +title +'\\n浣\x80\x85:'+authors +'\\nユ:'+source))
   	return;
  if ($("#username").val()=='')
  {
     alert("璇峰诲");
     location.href="../login.html";   
     return;
  }
   //寮\x80濮淇瀛\x98
   //collectPaper_exterior
   $.ajax({
	  type: "post",
	  url: "collectPaper_exterior.html", 
	  timeout:60000,
	  data:{title:title,authors:authors,source:source,date:year+'.'+'01',p_url:url,paperid:docs[i].id,detail:detail},
	  dataType: "text",
	  success:function(data){
		  if (data=="0") {
			  if (existalertcount==1)
			  	alert("宸插ㄧ稿璁烘璁板\x95!");existalertcount=2;
		  }
		  if (data=="1") {
			  if (succalertcount==1)
			  {alert("惰!");succalertcount=2;}
			  getcollectsnum();
		  }
		  if (data=="-1"){
			  if (failalertcount==1)
				  alert("惰澶辫触!");failalertcount=2;
		  }
	  },
	  error:function(){
	  //璇锋洪澶
	  alert("浣瓒!");
      }
	   

   });
}	

function highlight(content) //绾㈣插浣剧ず戒腑缁绱㈣
{
	if(typeof(querySeg)=="undefined")
		return content;
//	query = decodeURI(query); //unocode瑙ｇ锛濡涓瑙ｇ锛涓Unicode缂褰㈠锛娉归姹瀛\x97
	//疯缂%3A锛decodeURI澶浠舵娉瑙ｇ凤\xA5,\x80浠ヤ㈢挎㈢存ョ\xA8%3Aユ挎\x80\x82
//	strquery = query.replace(/title:|author:|author_exact:|organization:|keyword:|source:|"/g, "");
//	strquery = query.replace(/title%3A|author%3A|author_exact%3A|organization%3A|keyword%3A|source%3A|"/g, "");
		
//	strquery = $.trim(strquery);
//	key = strquery.split(" ");
 
	if(isPureEnglish(querySeg)){
		key = query.split(" ");
	}
	else{
		key = querySeg.split(" ");
	}
	var str = "";
	for ( var i = 0; i < key.length; i++) {
		key[i] = $.trim(key[i]);
		if(!isStopWord(key[i])){
			str += "|"+key[i];
		}
	}

	str = str.substring(1).replace(/[ ]|/g, "");
	oricontent = content;

	try {

	    //楂浜抽瀛锛涓轰腑娌℃辨ｆ疯璇涔存绌烘硷浠ュ椤讳娇ㄤ规ュ\x86
		if(isPureEnglish(str)){
			 strcontent = content.replace(eval("/\\\\b("+str+")\\\\b/ig"),"<font color=red>$1</font>"); //娉归涓锛涓轰腑璇璇涔存绌烘\xBC
		}
		else{
			strcontent = content.replace(eval("/("+str+")/ig"),"<font color=red>$1</font>");
		}
			 

	} catch (e) {
		strcontent = oricontent;
	}

	return strcontent;
}

/**
 * 辨瀛姣\x8D
 * @param str
 * @returns
 */
function isPureEnglish(str){
	var reg = /^[a-zA-Z\\\\s|]+$/;
	return reg.test(str);
}


function formatNumber(str){
	if(typeof(str)=='number')
		str=str+'';
	return str.replace(/\\d+?(?=(?:\\d{3})+$)/g, function(s){
		return s + ',';
	    });
}

function pageRender(result){
	var divHint=document.getElementById("divHint");
	var divContent=document.getElementById("divContent");
	var time=result.responseHeader.QTime;
	docs=result.response.docs;
	

	$('#res').hide();  
	$('#divselectbtns').show();
	$("#searchConditionForm").hide();
	
	numDocs=result.response.numFound;
	divHint.innerHTML="绱㈠\xB0"+formatNumber(numDocs)+"¤板锛ㄦ"+time+"ms";
	divContent.innerHTML="";
	if(numDocs==0) divContent.innerHTML="稿宠板\x95"; 
	else
	{
		$("#wrap").css("visibility", "visible");
		$("#frame_left").css("visibility", "visible");
	}
	generateYearList(result.facet_counts.facet_fields.year);
	generateTypeList(result.facet_counts.facet_fields.type);
	for (var doc in docs){
				
		//divContent.innerHTML+=showItem(docs[doc],doc,false);
		showSearchItem(docs[doc],doc,false)
		
	}
	$('.divItem').mouseover(function(e){$(this).addClass('divItemOver')});
	$('.divItem').mouseout(function(e){$(this).removeClass('divItemOver')});
	generatePages();
	
}

function generateYearList(yearlist){
	var showCount=10;
	var maxCount=30;
	var min=yearlist.length-showCount*2;
	if(min<0)
		min=0;
	$('#yearlist').html('');
	for(var i=yearlist.length-1;i>=min;){
		addyearlist(yearlist[i-1],yearlist[i]);
		i-=2;
	}
	
	$('#yearlistmore').hide();
	if(min>0)
		$('.yearListSwitch').show();
	else{
		$('.yearListSwitch').hide();
		return;
	}
	
	var min2=yearlist.length-maxCount*2;
	if(min2<0)
		min2=0;
	$('#yearlistmore').html('');
	for(var i=min-1;i>=min2;){
		addyearlistmore(yearlist[i-1],yearlist[i]);
		i-=2;
	}
	
}

function generateTypeList(list){

	if(list[5]>0){
		$('#bookNumber').html('('+list[5]+')');
		$('#bookNumber:parent').show();
	}
	else{
		$('#bookNumber:parent').hide();
	}
	
	if(list[9]>0){
		$('#conferenceNumber').html('('+list[9]+')');
		$('#conferenceNumber:parent').show();
	}
	else{
		$('#conferenceNumber:parent').hide();
	}
	
	if(list[11]>0){
		$('#conferencePaperNumber').html('('+list[11]+')');
		$('#conferencePaperNumber:parent').show();
	}
	else{
		$('#conferencePaperNumber:parent').hide();
	}
	
	if(list[7]>0){
		$('#bookChapterNumber').html('('+list[7]+')');
		$('#bookChapterNumber:parent').show();
	}
	else{
		$('#bookChapterNumber:parent').hide();
	} 
	
	if(list[15]>0){
		$('#journalNumber').html('('+list[15]+')');
		$('#journalNumber:parent').show();
	}
	else{
		$('#journalNumber:parent').hide();
	}
	
	if(list[17]>0){
		$('#journalPaperNumber').html('('+list[17]+')');
		$('#journalPaperNumber:parent').show();
	}
	else{
		$('#journalPaperNumber:parent').hide();
	}
	
	if(list[31]>0){
		$('#thesisNumber').html('('+list[31]+')');
		$('#thesisNumber:parent').show();
	}
	else{
		$('#thesisNumber:parent').hide();
	}
	
	if(list[33]>0){
		$('#unknownNumber').html('('+list[33]+')');
		$('#unknownNumber:parent').show();
	}
	else{
		$('#unknownNumber:parent').hide();
	}
	if(list[23] > 0){
		
		$("#referenceNumber").html('(' + list[23] + ')');
		$("#referenceNumber:parent").show();
	}else{
		
		$("#referenceNumber:parent").hide();
	}
}

var blnShowYearListMore=false;
function switchYearList(){
	if(blnShowYearListMore==false){
		$('#yearlistmore').show();
		$('.yearListSwitch').html('Less 芦');
	}
	else{
		$('#yearlistmore').hide();
		$('.yearListSwitch').html('More 禄');
	}
	blnShowYearListMore=!blnShowYearListMore;
}

function generatePages2(){
	var divPages=document.getElementById("divPages");
	var numPages=Math.ceil(numDocs/rows);
	if(numPages<=1){
		divPages.innerHTML='';
		return;
	}
	var url=window.location.href.replace(/&p=\\d+/,'');
	var str="";
	//涓涓椤\xB5
	if (curPage==1)
		str="<a href='"+url+"&p="+(curPage-1)+"' style='width:45px;height:20px;font-size:12px;text-align:center;'> 涓涓椤\xB5</a> " ;
	else
		str="<a href='"+url+"&p="+(curPage-1)+"' style='width:45px;height:20px;font-size:12px;text-align:center;'> 涓涓椤\xB5</a>";
	//椤垫
	var endPage=curPage+9;
	var startPage=curPage-9;
	if(endPage>numPages)
		endPage=numPages;
	if(startPage<1)
		startPage=1;
	for (var i=startPage; i<=endPage; i++) {
		if(i==curPage)
			str+="&nbsp;"+i+"&nbsp;&nbsp;";
		else
			str+="<a href='"+url+"&p="+i+"' style='text-align:center;'> "+i+" </a>";
	}
	//涓涓椤\xB5
	if(curPage+1<=numPages)
		str+="&nbsp;<a href='"+url+"&p="+(curPage+1)+"' style='width:45px;height:20px;font-size:12px;text-align:center;'> 涓涓椤\xB5</a>";
	else
		str+="&nbsp;涓涓椤\xB5";
	divPages.innerHTML=str;
}

function request(paras) {
	var url = decodeURI(location.href.replace(/%3A/g, ':'));
	var paraString = url.substring(url.indexOf("?") + 1, url.length).split("&");
	var paraObj = {}
	for (i = 0; j = paraString[i]; i++) {
		paraObj[j.substring(0, j.indexOf("=")).toLowerCase()] = j.substring(j
				.indexOf("=") + 1, j.length);
	}
	var returnValue = paraObj[paras.toLowerCase()];
	if (returnValue != null) {
		returnValue = returnValue.replace(/[+]/g, " ");
		returnValue = returnValue.replace(/[#]/g, " ");
		//returnValue = returnValue.replace(/[ m](\\d)/g, "");
		return (returnValue);
	} else {
		return null;
	}
}
    
// 淇瀛绔
function savepaper(i)
{

//峰璁烘稿充俊
//var key =$("#I_desc"+i).val().replace(/[ ]/g,"").split(".");
var key =$("#I_desc"+i).val().split("."); 

var authors=key[0];
var title=key[1];
//var source=key[2]+','+key[3];
var source=key[2];
var year=$("#I_year"+i).val();
var url=$("#I_url"+i).val();
var detail="<strong>抽璇\x8D:</strong>"+$("#I_keyword"+i).val()+"<br><strong>瑕:</strong>"+$("#I_abstract"+i).val();

title=title.replace(/["]/g,"");
title=title.replace(/[ ]/g,"");
source=source.replace(/["]/g,"");
source=source.replace(/[ ]/g,"");
if (selpapercount<=1)
{
var r=confirm("纭璁や瀛濡涓璁烘\x97?"+"\\n棰:"
+title
+'\\n浣\x80\x85:'+authors
+'\\nユ:'+source);
if (r==false)
return;
}

if ($("#username").val()=='')
{
alert("璇峰诲");
location.href="../login.html";   
}
else
{

//寮\x80濮淇瀛\x98
//SavePaper_exterio
$.ajax({
		  type: "post",
		  url: "SavePaper_exterio.html", 
		  timeout:60000,
		  data:{title:title,authors:authors,source:source,date:year+'.'+'01',p_url:url,detail:detail},
		  dataType: "text",
		  success:function(data){
			   if (data=="0") {
			    if (existalertcount==1)
			       {alert("宸插ㄧ稿璁烘璁板\x95!");existalertcount=2;}
			    }
		if (data=="1") {
		if (succalertcount==1)
		   {alert("淇瀛!");succalertcount=2;}
		getsavepapersnum();
		}
		if (data=="-1"){
		if (failalertcount==1)
		   {alert("淇瀛澶辫触!");failalertcount=2;}
		}          
		  },
		  error:function(){
		  //璇锋洪澶
		  alert("浣瓒!");
	      }
		   

});
}
}

function isStopWord(w){
	w=w.toLowerCase();
	for(var i in stopwords){
		if(stopwords[i]==w)
			return true;
	}
	return false;
}
var stopwords=['a', 'an', 'and', 'are', 'as', 'at', 'be', 'but', 'by', 'for', 'if', 'in', 'into', 'is', 'it', 'no', 'not', 'of', 'on', 'or', 'such', 'that', 'the', 'their', 'then', 'there', 'these', 'they', 'this', 'to', 'was', 'will', 'with'];

function comfirmRemoveDialog(elem,id){
	$("#confirmRemovePdfDialog").css("display","inline");
	$("#removePaperId").attr("value",id);
}


function showPrivilegeDialog(elem,id){
	$.ajax({
		type:"post",
		url:"getPdfPrivilege.html",
		timeout:60000,
		datatype:"text",
		data:{paperid:id},
		success:function(data){
			
			if(window.ActiveXObject){
				
			}else if(data instanceof Document){
				data=arguments[2].responseText;
			}
			if(data==='1'){
				$("#privilegeDialogRadio0").attr("checked","checked");
				//$("#privilegeDialogRadio1").attr("checked",false);
			}else{
				//$("#privilegeDialogRadio0").attr("checked",false);
				$("#privilegeDialogRadio1").attr("checked","checked");
			}
			$("#privilegeDialogHiddenId").attr("value",id);
			$("#privilegeDialog").css("display","inline");
			
		},
		error:function(){}
	});
	
}

function updatePdfPrivilege(elem){
	var id=$("#privilegeDialogHiddenId").val();
	var pdfPrivilege=$("input[name='pdfPrivilege']:checked").val();
	$.ajax({
		type:"post",
		url:"updatePdfPrivilege.html",
		timeout:60000,
		datatype:"text",
		data:{paperid:id,pdfPrivilege:pdfPrivilege},
		success:function(data){
			if(window.ActiveXObject){
				
			}else if(data instanceof Document){
				data=arguments[2].responseText;
			}
			$("#privilegeDialog").css("display","none");
			alert("淇规");
			
			
			
		},
		error:function(){}
	});
}

function closePrivilegeDialog(){
	$("#privilegeDialog").css("display","none");
}


function searchHomePage(){
	var urlFront = "http://paper.scholat.com/paper/select?callback=?&indent=on&version=2.2&json.wrf=searchHomePageResult&q=*:*";
	var urlBack ="&fl=*&sort=score desc,year desc&wt=json&facet=true&"
		+ "facet.field=type&facet.field=year&facet.sort=index&f.year.facet.mincount=1&facet.limit=-1";
	var url=urlFront+urlBack;
	
	$("#homePagePanel").tmpl({}).appendTo("#divContent");
	
	$.getJSON(url,searchHomePageResult);
	
}
function searchHomePageResult(result){
	console.log(result);
	$('#res').hide();  
	$('#divselectbtns').show();
	$("#searchConditionForm").hide();
	
	var numDocs=result.response.numFound;
	var time=result.responseHeader.QTime;
	divHint.innerHTML="辨"+formatNumber(numDocs)+"¤板锛ㄦ"+time+"ms";
	
	
	$("#wrap").css("visibility", "visible");
	$("#frame_left").css("visibility", "visible");
	
	generateYearList(result.facet_counts.facet_fields.year);
	generateTypeList(result.facet_counts.facet_fields.type);
}
function showSearchItem(doc,index,detail){
	//console.log(doc);
	var citation = highlight(doc.citation);
	var title = highlight(doc.title);
	var dateIndex = doc.timestamp.toString().indexOf('T');
	var date = doc.timestamp.toString().substring(0,dateIndex);
	//峰瑕\x84227涓瀛绗\xA6
	var abstractContent="";
	if(doc.abstract){
		var abstractLength = doc.abstract.length;
		if(abstractLength>230)
			abstractContent = highlight(doc.abstract.substring(0,227));
		else
			abstractContent = highlight(doc.abstract);
	}
	
	var authors = getAuthors(doc);
	var authorsLength =0;
	if(doc.author){
		authorsLength = doc.author.length;
	}
	
	var source = getSource(doc);
	var organization = highlight(doc.organization);
	
	var keyword = '';
	var keywordLength = 0;
	if(doc.keyword){
		keyword = getKeywords(doc);
		keywordLength = keyword.length;
	}
	var type='';
	if(doc.type=='Book')
		type='瀛涓';
	else
		type='句功绔';
	var startdate = '';
	var enddate = '';
	if(doc.enddate){
		enddate = doc.enddate.substring(0,10);
	}
	if(doc.startdate){
		startdate = doc.startdate.substring(0,10);
	}
	var duedate ='';
	if(doc.duedate){
		duedate = doc.duedate.substring(0,10);
	}
	//绗涓
	var emptyArgument4 = false;
	if(arguments[3]!== undefined&&arguments[3]!==null){
		emptyArgument4 = true;
	}
	var publisher = '';
	if(doc.publisher)
		publisher = highlight(doc.publisher);
	var school = '';
	if(doc.school)
		school = highlight(doc.school);
	var tmplDoc = {doc:doc,index:index,detail:false,citation:citation,title:title,date:date,
					abstractContent: abstractContent,authors:authors, source:source,
					organization:organization,abstractLength:abstractLength,keyword:keyword, 
					keywordLength:keywordLength,type:type,authorsLength:authorsLength,
					startdate:startdate, enddate:enddate, duedate:duedate, emptyArgument4:emptyArgument4,
					publisher:publisher, school:school};
	//divContent.innerHTML+=showItem(docs[doc],doc,false);
	$("#paperSearchResult").tmpl(tmplDoc).appendTo('#divContent');
	
}

function getQueryString(name) {
	var reg = new RegExp("(^|&)" + name + "=([^&]*)(&|$)", "i");
	var r = window.location.search.substr(1).match(reg);
	if (r != null) {
 return unescape(r[2]);
	}
	return null;
}
